Which algorithm to use to produce the im: 使用哪種算法生成圖像/Which algorithm to use to produce the image
Euler Ancestral - very creative, each ca: Euler A-非常有創意,每一張都可以根據步數得到完全不同的圖片,設置步數高于30-40沒用/Euler Ancestral - very creative, each can get a completely different picture depending on step count, setting steps higher than 30-40 does not help
How many times to improve the generated: 迭代改進生成的圖像多少次;更高的值需要更長的時間;非常低的值會產生不好的結果/How many times to improve the generated image iteratively; higher values take longer; very low values can produce bad results
生成可用于平鋪的圖像/Produce an image that can be tiled.

Number of sampling steps for upscaled pi: 設置進行高分辨率修復時的采樣迭代次數,0表示沿用原始采樣迭代次數/Number of sampling steps for upscaled picture. If 0, uses same as for original.
Determines how little respect the algori:
決定算法對圖像內容的影響程度。為0時,什么都不會改變。為1時,你講會得到一個毫不相關的圖像。
值低于1時,處理的迭代步數將少于"采樣步數"滑塊指定的步數/Determines how little respect the algorithm should have for image's content. At 0, nothing will change, and at 1 you'll get an unrelated image. With values below 1.0, processing will take less steps than the Sampling Steps slider specifies.
Adjusts the size of the image by multipl: 按比例放大原分辨率,單獨設定目標長寬時被忽略/Adjusts the size of the image by multiplying the original width and height by the selected value. Ignored if either Resize width to or Resize height to are non-zero.
Resizes image to this width. If 0, width: 將寬度調整到此值,0表示根據目標高度或放大倍率自適應調整/Resizes image to this width. If 0, width is inferred from either of two nearby sliders.
Resizes image to this height. If 0, heig: 將高度調整到此值,0表示根據目標寬度或放大倍率自適應調整/Resizes image to this height. If 0, height is inferred from either of two nearby sliders.
How many batches of images to create (ha: 創建多少批次的圖像(對生成性能和顯存占用沒有影響)/How many batches of images to create (has no impact on generation performance or VRAM usage)
How many image to create in a single bat: 每批創建多少圖像(提高生成性能和顯存占用)/How many image to create in a single batch (increases generation performance at cost of higher VRAM usage)
Classifier Free Guidance Scale - how str: 分類器引導系數-表示生成的圖像應該多大程度符合提示詞描述-值越低,生成的圖像越有創意/Classifier Free Guidance Scale - how strongly the image should conform to prompt - lower values produce more creative results
A value that determines the output of ra:
一個固定隨機數生成器輸出的值 - 以相同參數和隨機種子生成的圖像會得到相同的結果
🎲 將隨機種子設置為-1,則每次都會使用一個新的隨機數
♻️ 重用上一次使用的隨機種子,如果想要固定輸出結果就會很有用/A value that determines the output of random number generator - if you create an image with same parameters and seed as another image, you'll get the same result
Set seed to -1, which will cause a new r: 將隨機種子設置為 -1,則每次都會使用一個新的隨機數/Set seed to -1, which will cause a new random number to be used every time
Reuse seed from last generation, mostly: 重用上一次使用的隨機種子,如果想要固定結果就會很有用/Reuse seed from last generation, mostly useful if it was randomed
Seed of a different picture to be mixed: 將要參與生成的另一張圖的隨機種子/Seed of a different picture to be mixed into the generation.
How strong of a variation to produce. At: 想要產生多強烈的變化。設為 0 時,將沒有效果。設為 1 時,你將獲得完全產自差異隨機種子的圖像(此功能對帶有 a 后綴的采樣器無效)/How strong of a variation to produce. At 0, there will be no effect. At 1, you will get the complete picture with variation seed (except for ancestral samplers, where you will just get something).
Make an attempt to produce a picture sim: 嘗試生成與指定分辨率下相同圖像生成種子生成的圖像相似的圖像/Make an attempt to produce a picture similar to what would have been produced with same seed at specified resolution
Do not do anything special: 什么都不做/Do not do anything special
使用逗號分隔X軸的值/Separate values for X axis using commas.

使用逗號分隔Y軸的值/Separate values for Y axis using commas.
Open images output directory: 打開圖像輸出目錄/Open images output directory
Write image to a directory (default - lo: 將圖像寫入目錄(默認 - log/images)并將生成參數寫入 csv 表格文件/Write image to a directory (default - log/images) and generation parameters into csv file.
Resize image to target resolution. Unles: 將圖像大小調整為目標分辨率。除非高度和寬度匹配,否則你將獲得不正確的縱橫比/Resize image to target resolution. Unless height and width match, you will get incorrect aspect ratio.
Resize the image so that entirety of tar: 調整圖像大小,使整個目標分辨率都被圖像填充。裁剪多出來的部分/Resize the image so that entirety of target resolution is filled with the image. Crop parts that stick out.
Resize the image so that entirety of ima: 調整圖像大小,使整個圖像在目標分辨率內。用圖像的顏色填充空白區域/Resize the image so that entirety of image is inside target resolution. Fill empty space with image's colors.
How much to blur the mask before process: 處理前要對蒙版進行多強的模糊,以像素為單位/How much to blur the mask before processing, in pixels.
What to put inside the masked area befor: 在使用 Stable Diffusion 處理蒙版區域之前要在蒙版區域內放置什么/What to put inside the masked area before processing it with Stable Diffusion.
fill it with colors of the image: 用圖像的顏色(高強度模糊)填充它/fill it with colors of the image
keep whatever was there originally: 保留原來的圖像/keep whatever was there originally
fill it with latent space noise: 用潛空間噪聲填充/fill it with latent space noise
fill it with latent space zeroes: 用潛空間零填充/fill it with latent space zeroes
How many times to repeat processing an i: 重復處理一張圖像，并用作下一次迭代輸入的次數/How many times to repeat processing an image and using it as input for the next iteration
In loopback mode, on each loop the denoi: 在圖像迭代模式下,在每一次循環中,繪制強度都會乘以該值。小于1表示減少多樣性,所以你的圖像序列會逐漸收斂在固定的圖像上。大于1表示增加多樣性,所以你的圖像序列會變得越來越混亂/In loopback mode, on each loop the denoising strength is multiplied by this value. <1 means decreasing variety so your sequence will converge on a fixed picture. >1 means increasing variety so your sequence will become more and more chaotic.
For SD upscale, how much overlap in pixe: 使用SD放大時,貼圖之間應該有多少像素重疊。因為是切片重疊,所以當它們合并回一張圖像時,沒有清晰可見的接縫/For SD upscale, how much overlap in pixels should there be between tiles. Tiles overlap so that when they are merged back into one picture, there is no clearly visible seam.
A directory on the same machine where th: 服務器主機上某一目錄/A directory on the same machine where the server is running.
Leave blank to save images to the defaul: 留空將保存圖像到默認路徑/Leave blank to save images to the default path.
Result = A * (1 - M) + B * M: 結果=A*(1-M)+B*M/Result = A * (1 - M) + B * M
Regular expression; if weights's name ma: 與寫入內容名稱匹配的權重信息將不會寫入輸出的模型,可以通過寫入"^model_ema"以舍棄模型中的EMA信息/Regular expression; if weights's name matches it, the weights is not written to the resulting checkpoint. Use ^model_ema to discard EMA weights.

Use following tags to define how filenam: Use following tags to define how filenames for images are chosen: [steps], [cfg], [prompt_hash], [prompt], [prompt_no_styles], [prompt_spaces], [width], [height], [styles], [sampler], [seed], [model_hash], [model_name], [prompt_words], [date], [datetime], [datetime<Format>], [datetime<Format><Time Zone>], [job_timestamp]; leave empty for default.
If this option is enabled, watermark wil: 如果啟用此選項,水印將不會添加到生成出來的圖像中。警告:如果你不添加水印,你的行為可能是不符合專業操守的/If this option is enabled, watermark will not be added to created images. Warning: if you do not add watermark, you may be behaving in an unethical manner.
Use following tags to define how subdire: Use following tags to define how subdirectories for images and grids are chosen: [steps], [cfg],[prompt_hash], [prompt], [prompt_no_styles], [prompt_spaces], [width], [height], [styles], [sampler], [seed], [model_hash], [model_name], [prompt_words], [date], [datetime], [datetime<Format>], [datetime<Format><Time Zone>], [job_timestamp]; leave empty for default.
Restore low quality faces using GFPGAN n: 使用 GFPGAN 神經網絡修復低質量面部/Restore low quality faces using GFPGAN neural network
This regular expression will be used ext: 此正則表達式將用于從文件名中提取單詞,并將使用以下選項將它們接合到用于訓練的標簽文本中。留空以保持文件名文本不變/This regular expression will be used extract words from filename, and they will be joined using the option below into label text used for training. Leave empty to keep filename text as it is.
This string will be used to join split w: 如果啟用了上述選項,則此處的字符會用于將拆分的單詞接合為同一行/This string will be used to join split words into a single line if the option above is enabled.
Only applies to inpainting models. Deter: 僅適用于局部繪制專用的模型(模型后綴為 inpainting.ckpt 的模型)。決定了蒙版在局部繪制以及圖生圖中屏蔽原圖內容的強度。 1.0 表示完全屏蔽原圖,這是默認行為。0.0 表示完全不屏蔽讓原圖進行圖像調節。較低的值將有助于保持原圖的整體構圖,但很難遇到較大的變化/Only applies to inpainting models. Determines how strongly to mask off the original image for inpainting and img2img. 1.0 means fully masked, which is the default behaviour. 0.0 means a fully unmasked conditioning. Lower values will help preserve the overall composition of the image, but will struggle with large changes.
Early stopping parameter for CLIP model;: Early stopping parameter for CLIP model; 1 is stop at last layer as usual, 2 is stop at penultimate layer, etc.
When adding extra network such as Hypern: When adding extra network such as Hypernetwork or Lora to prompt, use this multiplier for it.
List of setting names, separated by comm: 設置項名稱的列表,以英文逗號分隔,該設置會移動到頂部的快速訪問欄,而不是默認的設置選項卡。有關設置名稱,請參見 modules/shared.py。需要保存設置并重啟才能應用/List of setting names, separated by commas, for settings that should go to the quick access bar at the top, rather than the usual setting tab. See modules/shared.py for setting names. Requires restarting to apply.
Comma-separated list of tab names; tabs: Comma-separated list of tab names; tabs listed here will appear in the extra networks UI first and in order lsited.
Cheap neural network approximation. Very: Cheap neural network approximation. Very fast compared to VAE, but produces pictures with 4 times smaller horizontal/vertical resolution and lower quality.
Very cheap approximation. Very fast comp: Very cheap approximation. Very fast compared to VAE, but produces pictures with 8 times smaller horizontal/vertical resolution and extremely low quality.
Ignores step count - uses a number of st: Ignores step count - uses a number of steps determined by the CFG and resolution
Denoising Diffusion Implicit Models - be: Denoising Diffusion Implicit models - 最擅長局部繪制/Denoising Diffusion Implicit Models - best at inpainting
If this values is non-zero, it will be a: 如果這個值不為零,它將被添加到隨機種子中,并在使用帶有 Eta 的采樣器時用于初始化隨機噪聲。你可以使用它來產生更多的圖像變化,或者你可以使用它來模仿其他軟件生成的圖像,如果你知道你在做什么/If this values is non-zero, it will be added to seed and used to initialize RNG for noises when using samplers with Eta. You can use this to produce even more variation of images, or you can use this to match images of other software if you know what you are doing.
Leave empty for auto: 留空時自動生成/Leave empty for auto
